**Summary:** This documentation covers Amplitude Experiment's Ruby SDK for both remote and local evaluation modes, including installation via gem/bundler, client initialization with deployment keys, fetching/evaluating variants for users, configuration options for timeouts/retries/polling intervals, cohort sync for local evaluation targeting, automatic assignment tracking, and Amplitude cookie parsing utilities.

